{"tid":177404,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩方法可以改善黑眼圈","createTime":"2017-03-28T23:43:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T00:08:49.000Z","uid":12805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c4fa045914401e1e1005d43f89185b95da9605ff","tid":177404,"uid":12805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T23:43:31.000Z","msg":"成日都比親戚同同學笑黑眼圈好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住諗住搽下啲聲稱可以淡到黑眼圈嘅嘢啦都好似無料到<br />\n早瞓諗住可以淡到啲啦，點知仲要比人話深過以前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無巴絲有啲方法可以真係淡到啲黑眼圈？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20730af1a67eb2e879e25cb7c3922fe5cfa5678","tid":177404,"uid":31788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T23:44:31.000Z","msg":"主要係血液循環唔好"},{"pid":"905cb3b1b886f27cd45c14e16344aa8c9ee55a29","tid":177404,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T23:46:38.000Z","msg":"冇架喇"},{"pid":"0c6513d92d4c25acb35658afecf6f030bfaaed93","tid":177404,"uid":12805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T23:47:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇架喇</blockquote><br />\n唔係幾想做一世超級熊貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"989c83b2c3dd72ad84c221c4e058eb357034eb1e","tid":177404,"uid":12805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T23:48:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>主要係血液循環唔好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪又係飲多啲水之類去改善呢樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e738a50d33865323a78597263baf63a4eb9501","tid":177404,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T00:29:54.000Z","msg":"鼻敏感都會<br />\n聽講"},{"pid":"f35a3ca0048f7fc2e6e792f142e34aa9927f56f3","tid":177404,"uid":53207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T00:34:05.000Z","msg":"我好細個已經有黑眼圈（有條青筋圍住）<br />\n又鼻敏感皮膚又薄<br />\n搽乜都冇用<br />\n遮又遮唔到<br />\n唔知做機果啲有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b326789deed53e27b04486cd2ab6eb72640f5866","tid":177404,"uid":40908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T00:34:37.000Z","msg":"做facial"},{"pid":"582e3efc8ca35732550a9251306dc220ec242d1f","tid":177404,"uid":12805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T00:36:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做facial</blockquote><br />\n我平時都有做呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係咪要做一段好長好長嘅時間先會見效<br />\n定係我做嗰個plan太廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"070a2e46310a21e0df00b0a3f06ee8992e2e72f6","tid":177404,"uid":12805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T00:37:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鼻敏感都會<br />\n聽講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁係咪要黑足一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 表示有鼻敏感"},{"pid":"72a4e2dbaf06f266a43fd6e3e13e767e8d89db03","tid":177404,"uid":12805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T00:38:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我好細個已經有黑眼圈（有條青筋圍住）<br />\n又鼻敏感皮膚又薄<br />\n搽乜都冇用<br />\n遮又遮唔到<br />\n唔知做機果啲有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  都想試下<br />\n我都遮唔到，所以好想知有咩實質嘅方法可以淡下嗰啲黑色"},{"pid":"fb66976c975b9b344a4168b1ba1481ce2d6595a7","tid":177404,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T00:39:21.000Z","msg":"早睡早起就可以<br />\n最好晚上9點睡"},{"pid":"ddc26063fdad265113e6236e8e90859394e37da7","tid":177404,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T00:52:14.000Z","msg":"果隻白眼圈有啲用，不過你唔好期望太大，黑眼圈跟我10幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ffe213e2e79d05e914024ddab444e5d0b2a174","tid":177404,"uid":12805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T00:56:01.000Z","msg":"<bloc